C ++********************************************************************
C                                                                      *
C SORTI.F           REMOVED FROM VODA            NOV 2011 ARDEAN LEITH *
C **********************************************************************
C=*                                                                    *
C=* This file is part of:   SPIDER - Modular Image Processing System.  *
C=* SPIDER System Authors:  Joachim FIRAnk & ArDean Leith               *
